      "review_summary": "The PR changes Discord terminal status-reaction cleanup to use configured `statusReactions.timing.doneHoldMs`/`errorHoldMs` values and adds a focused regression test.\n\nPR surface: Source +1, Tests +35. Total +36 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main passes configured Discord status-reaction timing into the controller but terminal cleanup still sleeps hardcoded default done/error hold values, and the linked issue includes real Discord observations. I did not run a live Discord repro in this read-only review.",
